genius.core.utility

Class UncertainAdditiveUtilitySpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • genius.core.utility.AbstractUtilitySpace
      • genius.core.utility.AdditiveUtilitySpace
        • genius.core.utility.UncertainAdditiveUtilitySpace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UtilitySpace, java.io.Serializable

    public class UncertainAdditiveUtilitySpace
extends AdditiveUtilitySpace
    UncertainAdditiveUtilitySpace is a serializable subset of bids in the bidspace with a full ordering: bid1<=bid2<=bid3...<=bidN. N is <= the total number of bids in the space. Part of the bids may be incorrectly placed depending on the error rate. Instead of containing these bids, this space contains an AdditiveUtilitySpace from which the N bids are generated.
